{{Quote|An infiltration team, then. My commandos are the best in the galaxy.|Crix Madine|<ref name="Moving Target" />}}
'''Rebel Commandos''',<ref name="Commander" /> also known as '''SpecForce soldiers''',<ref name="Forged in Battle">''[[Forged in Battle]]''</ref> were an elite variant of [[rebel trooper]]s of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic]].<ref name="Commander" /> They composed the multiple units of the [[Rebel Alliance Special Forces]] including the [[Marine Corps]], the [[Special Forces Trackers Unit]], and more.<ref name="Heroes">{{EncyclopediaCite|The Heroes of Rogue One}}</ref> Only a few members of the Alliance were able to arise to the commando level due to the training and resolve it took.<ref name="CommandosScene">{{AtomicMassGames|url=transmission/scene-to-stats-rebel-commandos|text=Scene to Stats: Rebel Commandos}}</ref>

